      "control_name": "S3 Access Grants Must Not Grant Broad Permissions",
      "control_description": "S3 Access Grants provide temporary credentials scoped to a bucket or prefix. An Access Grant with READWRITE permission on a broad scope (entire bucket or wildcard prefix) bypasses bucket policy restrictions.\n",
